videos.headline: Staley 'super proud' of Gamecocks after defeating UConn
videos.description: Dawn Staley explains how No. 1 South Carolina, led by Aliyah Boston (22 points, 15 rebounds), takes down No. 2 UConn in the Battle 4 Atlantis tournament.
